::Rex::

Rex looks at Battera, frowning. So far in his life, he had slagged most of 
the Predacons he had met, and at least shot at every single one. And now a 
Predacon was asking him to go eat fruit with her? He growls silently. There 
were better things to do than eat fruit with Preds, but if nothing else, he 
could keep an eye on her and make sure she didn't get into trouble.

"Allright. But I think you should tell Kluster whatever you need to tell him. 
I'm just an officer here."

He starts walking again, "Where did Chordate assign you to?"
